## Home Page
**Title:** View Completed Habits <br>
**Description:** **As a** user **I want** to see a section for completed habits on the homepage  
**So that** I can track what I have already achieved  

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- A “Completed Habits” section is visible on the homepage  
- It lists habits the user has marked as complete  
- The section updates in real time when new habits are completed  

**Priority:** Medium  
**Story Points:** 2  
